> **This platform gives Jia Hui more opportunities to find funding outside the local market. It can improve the company’s cash flow, support product development, and reduce her financial pressure.**

## Possible Limitations

> **The platform cannot guarantee successful investment. Jia Hui must provide accurate information, protect sensitive company data, and carefully review investment conditions before accepting an offer.**

